AppDirect,offers,a,platform,that,allows,businesses,to,find,web,based,software,solutions,for,their,needs,through,application,marketplaces,The,AppDirect,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,their,applications,into,the,Business,Application,Network,for,distribution,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML